msgstr "Visualização da reconciliação bancária"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:25
msgid ""
"To access a bank journal's **reconciliation view**, go to "
"your :guilabel:`Accounting Dashboard` and either:"
msgstr ""
"Para acessar a visualização de **reconciliação** de um extrato bancário, vá "
"para o :guilabel:`Painel do Financeiro` e escolha:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:28
msgid ""
"click the journal name (e.g., :guilabel:`Bank`) to display all transactions, "
"including those previously reconciled or"
msgstr ""
