"If you forgot to lock your tax date before clicking on :guilabel:`Closing "
"Journal Entry`, then Odoo automatically locks your fiscal period on the same "
"date as the accounting date of your entry. This safety mechanism can prevent "
"some fiscal errors, but it is advised to lock your tax date manually before, "
