#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:51
msgid ""
":ref:`E-invoicing (JoFotara)<localizations/jordan/jofotara>`: integration "
"for electronic invoicing in line with Jordanian government requirements"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Faturamento eletrônico (JoFotara)<localizations/jordan/jofotara>`: "
"integração para faturamento eletrônico de acordo com os requisitos do "
