#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:59
msgid ""
"The following :doc:`taxes <../accounting/taxes>` are available by default "
"with the Jordanian localization package:"
msgstr ""
"Os seguintes :doc:`impostos <../accounting/taxes>` estão disponíveis por "
