#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/luxembourg.rst:109
msgid ""
"In the :icon:`fa-folder-open` (:guilabel:`Partners`) selector, choose the "
"partners that fall under the exemption."
msgstr ""
"No seletor :icon:`fa-folder-open` (:guilabel:`Parceiros`), escolha os "
