#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:188
msgid "Veri*Factu"
msgstr "Veri*Factu"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:191
msgid ""
"Producers of Veri*Factu billing systems must self-certify their compliance "
"with the regulations. :download:`Download Odoo's \"declaración "
"responsable\"<spain/declaracion_responsable.pdf>`"
msgstr ""
"Os produtores de sistemas de faturamento Veri*Factu devem autocertificar sua "
"conformidade com as regulamentações. :download:`Baixe a \"declaración "
"responsable\" da Odoo<spain/declaracion_responsable.pdf>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:194
msgid ""
"**Veri*Factu** is the Spanish Tax Agency's verifiable invoice issuance "
"system. It is mandatory for most taxpayers in Spain, except for those who "
"use the SII system or are under a regional tax regime (i.e., TicketBai)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:198
msgid ""
"Odoo allows :ref:`invoices <localizations/spain/veri-factu-invoices>` and "
"Point of Sale :ref:`orders <localizations/spain/veri-factu-orders>` to be "
"automatically sent to the tax authorities."
msgstr ""
"O Odoo permite que :ref:`faturas <localizations/spain/veri-factu-invoices>` "
"e :ref:`pedidos <localizations/spain/veri-factu-orders>` do Ponto de Venda "
"sejam enviados automaticamente às autoridades fiscais."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:206
msgid "To enable **Veri\\*Factu**, follow these steps:"
msgstr "Para habilitar o **Veri\\*Factu**, siga estas etapas:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:208
msgid ""
"Open the Settings app to make sure your company's :guilabel:`Country` "
"and :guilabel:`Tax ID` are correctly set in the :ref:`Companies <general/"
"companies/company>` section."
msgstr ""
"Abra o aplicativo Configurações para garantir que o :guilabel:`País` e o "
":guilabel:`Tax ID` da sua empresa estejam configurados corretamente na seção "
":ref:`Empresas <general/companies/company>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:210
msgid ""
":ref:`Install <general/install>` the :guilabel:`Spain - Veri*Factu` "
"(`l10n_es_edi_verifactu`) module."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:212
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings` "
"or :menuselection:`Invoicing --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll to "
"the :guilabel:`Veri\\*Factu` section, check the :guilabel:`Enable "
"Veri*Factu` option, and click :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Manage "
"certificates` to add a certificate."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:216
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Certificates for Veri\\*Factu` list view, "
"click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Na exibição de lista :guilabel:`Certificates for Veri\\*Factu`, clique em "
":guilabel:`Novo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:217
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Upload your file`, then select a certificate file and enter "
"the :guilabel:`Password` needed to open the certificate (if there is one)."
msgstr ""
"Clique em :guilabel:`Upload your file`, selecione um arquivo de certificado "
"e insira a :guilabel:`Senha` necessária para abrir o certificado (se houver "
"uma)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:221
msgid "At least one certificate has to be uploaded."
msgstr "Pelo menos um certificado deve ser carregado."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:222
msgid ""
"By default Veri*Factu is in testing mode. The data is sent to test servers "
"and is not considered official. When official data can be sent to the "
"production servers, go to the :guilabel:`Veri\\*Factu` section in "
"the :guilabel:`Settings` and disable :guilabel:`Test Environment`."
msgstr ""
"Por padrão, o Veri*Factu está no modo de teste. Os dados são enviados para "
"servidores de teste e não são considerados oficiais. Quando os dados "
"oficiais puderem ser enviados para os servidores de produção, vá para a "
"seção :guilabel:`Veri\\*Factu` nas :guilabel:`Configurações` e desabilite "
":guilabel:`Test Environment`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:232
msgid ""
"Once an :doc:`invoice <../../finance/accounting/customer_invoices>` is "
"confirmed, it can be :ref:`sent <accounting/invoice/sending>`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Send` window, the Veri*Factu option is available if "
"Veri*Factu has been enabled."
msgstr ""
"Depois que uma :doc:`fatura <../../finance/accounting/customer_invoices>` "
"for confirmada, ela pode ser :ref:`enviada <accounting/invoice/sending>`. Na "
"janela :guilabel:`Enviar`, a opção Veri*Factu fica disponível se o "
"Veri*Factu tiver sido habilitado."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:236
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Send` to generate a JSON file containing the invoice "
"details. This file is stored as a Veri*Factu document. In "
"the :guilabel:`Veri*Factu` tab, all corresponding documents are listed by "
"their creation date and current status."
msgstr ""
"Clique em :guilabel:`Enviar` para gerar um arquivo JSON contendo os detalhes "
"da fatura. Este arquivo é armazenado como um documento Veri*Factu. Na aba "
":guilabel:`Veri*Factu`, todos os documentos correspondentes são listados por "
"sua data de criação e status atual."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:241
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:266
msgid ""
"To download a JSON file, click on its document in the :guilabel:`Veri*Factu` "
"tab. Then, in the :guilabel:`Open: Veri*Factu Documents` window, click the "
"link in the :guilabel:`JSON` field."
msgstr ""
"Para baixar um arquivo JSON, clique em seu documento na aba "
":guilabel:`Veri*Factu`. Em seguida, na janela :guilabel:`Abrir: Documentos "
"Veri*Factu`, clique no link no campo :guilabel:`JSON`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:245
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:270
msgid ""
"The document should be sent to the :abbr:`AEAT (Agencia Estatal de "
"Administración Tributaria)` immediately. However, it may be delayed due to "
"mandatory waiting periods between submissions required by the :abbr:`AEAT "
"(Agencia Estatal de Administración Tributaria)`. In such cases, the document "
"is automatically sent the next time a scheduled action runs."
msgstr ""
"O documento deve ser enviado para a :abbr:`AEAT (Agencia Estatal de "
"Administración Tributaria)` imediatamente. No entanto, pode haver atraso "
"devido aos períodos de espera obrigatórios entre os envios exigidos pela "
":abbr:`AEAT (Agencia Estatal de Administración Tributaria)`. Nesses casos, o "
"documento é enviado automaticamente na próxima vez que uma ação agendada for "
"executada."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:249
msgid ""
"A Veri\\*Factu **QR code** appears on the invoice PDF. Scan this code to "
"verify that the invoice has been received and recognized by the :abbr:`AEAT "
"(Agencia Estatal de Administración Tributaria)`."
msgstr ""
"Um **código QR** Veri\\*Factu aparece no PDF da fatura. Digitalize este "
"código para verificar se a fatura foi recebida e reconhecida pela "
":abbr:`AEAT (Agencia Estatal de Administración Tributaria)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:256
msgid "Point of sale orders"
msgstr "Pedidos do ponto de venda"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:258
msgid ""
"Once an order has been :ref:`paid <pos/sell>`, a JSON file containing the "
"order details is generated. This file is stored as a Veri*Factu document."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:261
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Orders --> Orders`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Orders` list view, select the relevant order. In "
"the :guilabel:`Veri*Factu` tab, all the corresponding documents are listed "
"by their creation date and current status."
msgstr ""
"Vá para :menuselection:`Ponto de Venda --> Pedidos --> Pedidos`. Na exibição "
"de lista :guilabel:`Pedidos`, selecione o pedido relevante. Na aba "
":guilabel:`Veri*Factu`, todos os documentos correspondentes são listados por "
"sua data de criação e status atual."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:275
msgid ""
"If an invoice is generated for an order during the payment process, the "
"Veri*Factu document is :ref:`created and sent for the invoice <localizations/"
"spain/veri-factu-invoices>` instead."
msgstr ""
"Se uma fatura for gerada para um pedido durante o processo de pagamento, o "
"documento Veri*Factu será :ref:`criado e enviado para a fatura "
"<localizations/spain/veri-factu-invoices>` em vez disso."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:279
msgid ""
"A Veri\\*Factu **QR code** appears on the order receipt, even if an invoice "
"is created for the order. Scan this code to verify that the invoice has been "
"received and recognized by the :abbr:`AEAT (Agencia Estatal de "
"Administración Tributaria)`"
msgstr ""
"Um **código QR** Veri\\*Factu aparece no recibo do pedido, mesmo se uma "
"fatura for criada para o pedido. Escaneie este código para verificar se a "
