":guilabel:`Segredo do Hash Seguro`, e a :guilabel:`Moeda` na aba "
":guilabel:`Configuração` com os valores que você salvou na etapa "
":ref:`payment_providers/asiapay/configure_dashboard`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/asiapay.rst:0
msgid ""
"By default, the payment provider AsiaPay is configured to verify the secret "
"hash with the hash function `SHA1`. If a different function is :ref:`set on "
"your account <payment_providers/asiapay/configure_dashboard>`, activate "
"the :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>` and set the same value to the "
"field :guilabel:`Secure Hash Function` in the :guilabel:`Credentials` tab."
msgstr ""
"Por padrão, o provedor de pagamento AsiaPay está configurado para verificar "
"o hash secreto com a função de hash `SHA1`. Se uma função diferente estiver "
":ref:`definida em sua conta <payment_providers/asiapay/configure_dashboard>"
"`, ative o :ref:`modo de desenvolvedor <developer-mode>` e defina o mesmo "
"valor no campo :guilabel:`Função de Hash Seguro` na aba "
":guilabel:`Credenciais`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:3
msgid "Authorize.Net"
msgstr "Authorize.Net"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:5
msgid ""
"`Authorize.Net <https://www.authorize.net>`_ is a United States-based online "
"payment solution provider, allowing businesses to accept **credit cards**."
msgstr ""
"O `Authorize.Net <https://www.authorize.net>`_ é um provedor de soluções de "
"pagamento online com sede nos Estados Unidos, permitindo que as empresas "
"aceitem **cartões de crédito**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:17
msgid ""
"Odoo needs your **API Credentials & Keys** to connect with your "
"Authorize.Net account, which comprise:"
msgstr ""
"O Odoo precisa de suas **Credenciais e Chaves de API** para se conectar com "
"sua conta Authorize.Net, que incluem:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:20
msgid ""
"**API Login ID**: The ID solely used to identify the account with "
"Authorize.Net."
msgstr ""
"**API Login ID**: O ID usado exclusivamente para identificar a conta no "
"Authorize.Net."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:21
msgid "**API Transaction Key**"
msgstr "**API Transaction Key**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:22
msgid "**API Signature Key**"
msgstr "**API Signature Key**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:23
msgid "**API Client Key**"
msgstr "**API Client Key**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:25
msgid ""
"To retrieve them, log into your Authorize.Net account, go "
"to :menuselection:`Account --> Settings --> Security Settings --> API "
"Credentials & Keys`, generate your **Transaction Key** and **Signature "
"Key**, and paste them on the related fields in Odoo. Then, click on "
"**Generate Client Key**."
msgstr ""
"Para recuperá-los, faça login na sua conta Authorize.Net, acesse "
":menuselection:`Account --> Settings --> Security Settings --> API "
"Credentials & Keys`, gere sua **Transaction Key** e **Signature Key**, e "
"cole-as nos campos relacionados no Odoo. Em seguida, clique em **Generate "
"Client Key**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:31
msgid ""
"To test Authorize.Net with a *sandbox* account, change the :guilabel:`State` "
"to :guilabel:`Test Mode`. We recommend doing this on a test Odoo database, "
"rather than on your main database."
msgstr ""
"Para testar o Authorize.Net com uma conta *sandbox*, altere o "
":guilabel:`State` para :guilabel:`Test Mode`. Recomendamos fazer isso em um "
"banco de dados de teste do Odoo, em vez de no seu banco de dados principal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:34
msgid ""
"If you use the :guilabel:`Test Mode` with a regular account, it results in "
"the following error: *The merchant login ID or password is invalid or the "
"account is inactive*."
msgstr ""
"Se você usar o :guilabel:`Test Mode` com uma conta regular, resultará no "
"seguinte erro: *The merchant login ID or password is invalid or the account "
"is inactive*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:38
msgid "Configuration tab"
msgstr "Guia de configuração"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:41
msgid "Place a hold on a card"
msgstr "Colocar um cartão em espera"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:43
msgid ""
"With Authorize.Net, you can enable the :ref:`manual capture "
"<payment_providers/manual_capture>`. If enabled, the funds are reserved for "
"30 days on the customer's card, but not charged yet."
msgstr ""
"Com o Authorize.Net, você pode habilitar a :ref:`captura manual "
"<payment_providers/manual_capture>`. Se habilitado, os fundos são reservados "
"por 30 dias no cartão do cliente, mas ainda não cobrados."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:48
msgid ""
"After **30 days**, the transaction is **voided automatically** by "
"Authorize.Net."
msgstr ""
"Após **30 dias**, a transação é **anulada automaticamente** pelo "
"Authorize.Net."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:56
msgid "ACH payments (USA only)"
msgstr "Pagamentos ACH (apenas EUA)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:58
msgid ""
":abbr:`ACH (automated clearing house)` is an electronic funds transfer "
"system used between bank accounts in the United States."
msgstr ""
":abbr:`ACH (automated clearing house)` é um sistema de transferência "
"eletrônica de fundos usado entre contas bancárias nos Estados Unidos."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:64
msgid ""
"To give customers the possibility to pay using ACH, `sign up for "
"Authorize.Net eCheck's service <https://www.authorize.net/payments/"
"echeck.html>`_. Once eCheck is activated, duplicate the previously "
"configured Authorize.Net payment provider on Odoo by going "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Payment Providers --> "
"Authorize.net`. Then, click the cog icon (:guilabel:`⛭`) and "
"select :guilabel:`Duplicate`. Change the provider's name to differentiate "
"both versions (e.g., `Authorize.net - Banks`)."
msgstr ""
"Para dar aos clientes a possibilidade de pagar usando ACH, `inscreva-se no "
"serviço eCheck do Authorize.Net <https://www.authorize.net/payments/"
"echeck.html>`_. Uma vez que o eCheck esteja ativado, duplique o provedor de "
"pagamento Authorize.Net previamente configurado no Odoo acessando "
":menuselection:`Financeiro --> Configuração --> Provedores de Pagamento --> "
"Authorize.net`. Em seguida, clique no ícone de engrenagem (:guilabel:`⛭`) e "
"selecione :guilabel:`Duplicar`. Altere o nome do provedor para diferenciar "
"as duas versões (por exemplo, `Authorize.net - Bancos`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:71
msgid ""
"When ready, change the provider's :guilabel:`State` to :guilabel:`Enabled` "
"for a regular account or :guilabel:`Test Mode` for a sandbox account."
msgstr ""
"Quando estiver pronto, altere o :guilabel:`State` do provedor para "
":guilabel:`Enabled` para uma conta regular ou :guilabel:`Test Mode` para uma "
"conta sandbox."

